Package: robscout
Title: Robust Covariance-Regularized Regression
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Maggie", "Liu", , "yitong.liu@stat.ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-8713-1722"))
Description: This package implements the robust covariance-regularized 
    regression method. It is a robust version of the Scout method, introduced
    by Witten and Tibshirani (2009). 
